{"tid":1902543,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會過半，除左否決正苦議案同惡法，仲有唔駛再見到梁君彥同陳健波做主席","createTime":"2020-02-28T11:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T04:21:52.000Z","uid":179718,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2b87b12a87b865c239584132a336d3f151ccf1cc","tid":1902543,"uid":179718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:38:54.000Z","msg":"少數派因為立法會過半<br />\n先可以把持晒立法會、財委會同事務委員會(最重要嗰幾個)主席<br />\n然後好似施捨咁俾番副主席你做<br />\n但根本佢地先係真正嘅少數派<br />\n我地先有真正民意授權<br />\n<br />\n我地點解仲要容忍梁君彥同陳健波<br />\n鍾意用幾多時間去審議議案<br />\n鐘意剪布就剪布<br />\n鍾意就限制議員嘅發言時間<br />\n仲有最不幸嘅係<br />\n點解教人蒸口罩嘅元秋可以做到衞生事務委員會主席<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因為少數派喺立法會過半呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以立法會過半係非常重要<br />\n所有話投白票同話唔好再繼續議會抗爭<br />\n根本只係想<br />\n繼續通過正苦嘅議案同惡法<br />\n繼續俾梁君彥同陳健波呢兩條友繼續做主席<br />\n繼續俾元秋之流把持各個事務委員會主席"},{"pid":"eb0e6c806c7ebc552d335b3cbaf0b2d81de07139","tid":1902543,"uid":15647,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:41:20.000Z","msg":"我想講上屆主席本身係梁耀忠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c18c3ad9cc055284e97198b37aaade60a51cd6f","tid":1902543,"uid":179718,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eb0e6c806c7ebc552d335b3cbaf0b2d81de07139","tid":1902543,"uid":15647,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:41:20.000Z","msg":"我想講上屆主席本身係梁耀忠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:43:49.000Z","msg":"梁耀忠邊係主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢只係未選出主席前嘅代主席<br />\n代主席只係用黎選主席"},{"pid":"3aa3de7318b42d296249d4a4